				<wikidot:authorName>Klurg</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2827333</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This has that nice series 1 feel. It's simple, yet effective and it has some comedy, not too much or the type that makes the Foundation's workers seem incompetent, but just the right amount. Mind you, the premise is a bit unoriginal, but everything else overshadows that. And no, I don't consider a little of what others consider LolFoundation a problem.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
