				<wikidot:authorName>Sharptoe</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1991761</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Note: All personnel are requested to stop referring to SCP-080 as &quot;The Boogieman&quot;. - Dr. ██████</p> </blockquote> <p>This got a chuckle out of me.</p> <p>Some may see this as a tonal break. I see it as a masterful injection of humour in a situation where the reader will be emotionally susceptible.</p> 
				 	]]>
